July 28, 2017 10:57 PM ET
Insurance

Company Overview of Harel Insurance Company Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Harel Insurance Company Ltd. provides general and life insurance solutions. Its solutions include provident and pension funds, as well as health, travel, homeowner’s, business, and motor insurance. It was formerly known as Shiloah Insurance Company Ltd. and changed its name to Harel Insurance Company Ltd. in 2003. The company was founded in 1933 and is based in Ramat-Gan, Israel. Harel Insurance Company Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Delek Drilling - Limited Partnership.


