harel insurance co ltd
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Insurance
Sub-Industry: Life Insurance
Harel Insurance Company Ltd. provides comprehensive financial and insurance solutions. The Company offers life insurance, general insurance, health insurance, provident funds, pension funds, mutual funds, ETFs, and investment portfolio management. Harel Insurance serves customers throughout Israel.




